text: Joanna Hughes (born 22 December 1977) is an Australian gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Australia Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Melbourne Category:Commonwealth Games medallists in gymnastics Category:Commonwealth Games bronze medallists for Australia
